  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV91">
<l>curuṅkuṟi veṇṇey toṭuvuṇṭa kaḷvaṉai vaiyamuṟṟu</l>
<l>moruṅkuṟa vuṇṭa peruvayiṟ ṟāḷaṉai māvalimāṭ</l>
<l>ṭiruṅkuṟa ḷāki yicaiyavōr mūvaṭi vēṇṭicceṉṟa</l>
<l>peruṅkiṟi yāṉaiyal lālaṭi yēṉeñcam pēṇalatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The thief who dug into [and] ate the butter from the shrinking net,</l>
<l>the big-bellied man who ate the whole world, to have it together, the great trickster</l>
<l>who went, desiring once three steps, to the great Bali, [and] when he agreed,</l>
<l>became a huge dwarf, the heart of me, [his] servant esteems nothing but him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
